name: TMT SysML Model
tagline: Thirty Meter Telescope System Model in SysML
body:
### Welcome to the Thirty Meter Telescope SysML model
Thirty Meter Telescope System Model in SysML This is the SysML system model of the Thirty Meter Telescope project ([www.tmt.org](www.tmt.org)). An overview of system level simulation in general and the purpose of this model in particular you can find in this [video](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MLa8IVuJeBc)
